Text: Information on Standardized Master Power Contractand the EEI Alliance of Energy Suppliers will sponsor a special workshop on November in Washington DC to address the wholesale trading market and Standardized Master Power Contract Attached is a PDF file of the Workshop brochure You must have an Acrobat reader to open it If you do not you may go to to download a gratis version If you would prefer you may contact Trish Higgins the Alliance Coordinator and she will be pleased to fax a copy to your office For your information you will also receive a copy via mail As shown on the the PDF file but not the printed brochure Harlan Murphy of Dynegy Power Marketing Inc will participate on the panel Can the Standardized Contract Assist the Market Pwrmktpdf
